original: Holmedal, Frans Edvin, kyrkoherde, S’t:enkyrk!a, f. 1,1/12/14 i Rödbo, Gbgs o. Boh. 1. G. 40 m. Ing-Marie Svennberg. Barn: Agneta f. 44, Lars 46. — Teol. fil. ex. 35, teol. kand. samt prakt. teol. prov 39. Tj igjort som e. o. prästman i Bokenäs, Länghem o. Kungsbacka, kyrkoadj. i Visby 41, domkyr ko syssloman där 43, kyrkoh. i Stenkyrka sed. 44.
translated: Holmedal, Frans Edvin, parish priest, Stenkyrka, born January 1, 1914 in Rödbo, Gothenburg and Bohuslän. Married Ing-Marie Svennberg in 1940. Their children are Agneta born in 1944 and Lars born in 1946. He passed his fil. theology exam in 1935, theology candidate and practical theology exam in 1939. He worked as an assistant pastor in Bokenäs, Länghem, and Kungsbacka, a church clerk in Visby in 1943, and a parish priest in Stenkyrka since 1944.
